               stealing, on the <rs id="t17940716-43-cd215" type="crimeDate">7th of June</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17940716-43-off214 t17940716-43-cd215"></join>, three silver table spoons, value 1l. 10s. a silver gravy spoons, value 15s. a silver pepper castor, value 5s. the goods of 
                     <persName id="t17940716-43-victim442" type="victimName">
                        Samuel 
                        Hillier
                     <interp inst="t17940716-43-victim442" type="surname" value="Hillier"></interp>
