                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17940716-43-defend441 t17940716-43-punish218"></join>
               Death
            </rs>. (Aged 20.)</p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
